  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n\r\nCurrently the stock implementation of ERC777 do not adjust the `defaultOperators()` return values over time, when there is revokings of the default operators.\r\n\r\nI find the usage of `EnumerableSet.AddressSet` could improve the implementation here.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nUse `EnumerableSet.AddressSet private _defaultOperators` to replace all default operators related code.\r\n\r\n",
